<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Hata ndimi elfu elfu,
 Hazitoshi kweli
 Bwana Yesu kumsifu,
 Kwa zake fadhili.

[V2]
 Yesu, jina liwezalo
 Kufukuza hofu;
 Lanifurahisha hilo,
 Lanipa wokovu.

[V3]
 Jina hilo ni uzima;
 Ni afya amani;
 Laleta habari njema;
 Twalipiwa deni.

[V4]
 Yesu huvunja mapingu
 Ya dhambi moyoni;
 Msamaha, tena nguvu,
 Twapata rohoni.

[V5]
 Kwa sauti yake vile
 Wafu hufufuka
 Wakafurahi milele,
 Pasipo mashaka.

[V6]
 Ewe Yesu wangu Bwana,
 Uwezo nipewe,
 Kuhubiri kote sana,
 Wote wakujue.

[C1]
   Hallelujah kwa Bwana
   Alikufa kalvari
   Halle Halle Hallelujah
   Hallelujah Amen</lyrics>
<title>Hata Ndimi Elfu TZR3</title>
<hymn_number>3</hymn_number>
</song>